{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_13", "eventName": "惡兆湍流", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "13-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "傭兵一日", "storyInfo": "幻境散去，幾人看到了一座血色法陣。赫德雷得知了巫妖在為卡茲戴爾準備拆分撤離計劃，而後向埃芒加德提出，他會奪取“生命線”，以這種能夠遠距離傳送的手段幫助薩卡茲們回家。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"maskid": "ui_cutin_mask_vertical", "style": 1.0, "size": "600, 720", "offset": "-120,0", "channel": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "type": 2.0, "name": "43_g8_wildernesswarcircle", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "aduration": 3.0, "sfrom": "1.9,1.9", "sto": "1.9,1.9", "sduration": 0.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "type": 1.0, "slot": "m", "offset": "-120,50", "name": "cutin_char_5", "sfrom": "1.2,1.2", "sto": "1.2,1.2", "aduration": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "type": 1.0, "slot": "m", "pfrom": "-120,50", "pto": "-170,50", "duration": 40.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我從沒這麼明白地感覺到，我的血在自己的血管裡流動。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n它們橫衝亂撞，穿過四肢，最終在我的心臟裡匯聚。 ", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "在羅德島，那些醫療幹員幫我做檢查的時候，想給我打一種……那東西叫什麼來著，我忘了。 ", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我嚇唬了他們一頓，我可不想自己的身體裡除了源石，還要再混上些什麼亂七八糟的東西。 ", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n好吧，現在我知道了，我們的確靠著這些血來活著。 ", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "攜帶氧氣什麼的，赫德雷和我講過。 ", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n不過現在，我恨這種感覺。 ", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "你們既然是我的血，那就要聽我的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n否則，就滾出我的身體。 ", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我摸向腰間的刀。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_daggerexsheath", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_inject", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "bld"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "bld", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "43_g8_wildernesswarcircle", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈——", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，到底怎麼了！", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#6$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，放血療法。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#6$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "赫德雷皺著眉頭，那巫妖也正緊緊抓著自己的帽子。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n躁動終於平息了。不，應該說，是頑強的我們適應了。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲，你還好嗎？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一點事都沒有。你們該給我解釋一下。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#14$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我懂了，這些石頭對冷酷的老女人無效。凱爾希絕對能在這裡跳舞。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信她可以，我建議你先把傷口包紮好。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我刺得很準，避過了動脈。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，這是針對薩卡茲的裝置？與血液有關？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#14$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲，血，呵，還真是難猜。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些巫術裝置……還沒有真正啟動。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……因為有一些不安的感覺而靠近這裡，原來這就是元兇。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#8$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也難怪老師們對待倫蒂尼姆的事情總是謹慎過頭。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#8$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那真正啟動起來會怎麼樣？所有薩卡茲爆體而亡？然後血魔大君就會用我們的血潑那些維多利亞人一身？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "附近……沒有車轍，沒有運輸痕跡。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#8$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們就把這些巨大的結晶，跨過遙遠的距離，直接投放到了這裡？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#4$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我好像不是第一次聽說這種手段。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#4$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃芒加德女士……這似乎也與您無關吧。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。巫妖沒辦法做到這樣的事，我們研究的，不是此處的“空間”。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，您剛才似乎，認出我來了？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷嘛……我注意到過你的書，有些手抄本甚至流傳到了萊塔尼亞的薩卡茲之中。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您有什麼線索嗎？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為什麼要幫你們？你剛炸掉了我的小方塊。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#7$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "嘖。這女人剛才斜了我一眼。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我至少沒往你胸口的那個洞裡塞炸彈。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯哼。現在的薩卡茲雇傭兵都這麼急於求死嗎？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#7$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "她要是再說一句，我就真的那麼做。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……算了。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "談到剛才的幻境。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是些殘跡……空間的，時間的。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們剛才在找轍痕？幻境就是轍痕。某種特殊的法術影響了這裡。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那不是源石技藝，不是薩卡茲巫術。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些法陣確實與血魔有關，而幻境也確實和法陣有關，但又沒有直接聯繫。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定……你會用到這些線索呢？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……巫妖們的態度是什麼？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和往常一樣，沒有任何允諾。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可有線人告訴我，卡茲戴爾最近……也出現了一些巫妖，你們平時可不怎麼在卡茲戴爾亮相。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哦？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你離開巴別塔，然後加入感染者組織，最後來到倫蒂尼姆，卻還能在卡茲戴爾留下情報網路？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的只是個僱傭兵？我覺得你的才幹，至少能在萊塔尼亞撈個金律法衛當當。哦，就是你的法術不太厲害。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "個人習慣。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#8$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯哼。“個人習慣”。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片戰場如此寬廣，如果我真有意悄無聲息地離開，你覺得憑你們能攔得住我？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您……也在找我們？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#4$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是吧。我對你有點興趣。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們薩卡茲聊天一定要繞圈子嗎？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "伊內絲第一次插話了。她不耐煩了，很好。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "她吸引了注意，我來弄死這個什麼巫妖。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你都能收到卡茲戴爾的消息，那對兄妹自然只是視而不見。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們需要，嗯，為特雷西斯準備一些，後手。我們正在接管卡茲戴爾。大家都來維多利亞了，總得有人照看著點老家。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼後手，慶功宴嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，這是計劃的第一部分。再立個建國日之類的。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，不開玩笑了——", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——這確實就是計劃的第一部分。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特雷西斯和特蕾西婭絲毫沒有撤退的打算，他們似乎真的想要把倫蒂尼姆變成和整片大地決戰的戰場。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也不知道他們究竟哪來的自信，但既然是他們兩兄妹的計劃，就一定有早就準備好的手段。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，如果他們真的成功了——我們將確實地重建卡茲戴爾，重建薩卡茲的樂土。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……如果失敗了呢？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果薩卡茲在這裡遭遇了失敗，那我們損失的，將是一整代年輕人，也許還有未來所有的年輕人。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在兩百年前的那場遠征之後，大部分國家對卡茲戴爾的現狀並不了解，也不感興趣。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到現在，維多利亞的許多上位者還以為卡茲戴爾不過是一片廢墟。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但內戰前，在特蕾西婭殿下的建設之下，卡茲戴爾已經有了移動城市的雛形。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但特雷西斯攪亂了一切。卡茲戴爾現在不過是個超級巨大的巫術機器罷了，一邊走還一邊往下掉零件的那種。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾根本扛不住所謂的戰爭，而攝政王恰恰還掀起了一場戰爭。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在開戰以後，各方的探子一定已經開始接觸卡茲戴爾。那些作壁上觀的國家，又會怎麼看待領土內的……薩卡茲們？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，你是個悲觀的人。挺好的，我也是。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，計劃的第二部分——現在留在卡茲戴爾的巫妖已經做好了拆分卡茲戴爾的計劃。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果特雷西斯失敗，卡茲戴爾將會立刻被分割為幾塊，甚至十幾塊……", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶著附屬的居民區，按照劃分好的，呃，“氏族”單位，藏進荒野的深處。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "規劃路線，平衡生產，確保卡茲戴爾變成移動城市這件事不是毫無意義。對薩卡茲而言，其他人類的敵意就是天災。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾將會迎來又一個流亡時代。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "又是流亡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n說什麼廢話，難道我們現在沒在流亡嗎？我們是在哪座移動城市上安居樂業看著天災雲喝下午茶了？", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲已經緊緊團結在了一起，雖然並非以我期望的方式……但就結果而言，特雷西斯做到了。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但團結的意義，可以不僅僅是又一次復仇和殺戮。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕這種團結是建立在仇恨和戰爭上？這可不容易啊，赫德雷大哥。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾不僅是一座城市，還是每一個把那裡視為家的人。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在原本的計劃裡，卡茲戴爾不需要很多居民……他們也不可能允許我們帶走很多人。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們需要結束這場在維多利亞的戰爭，越早越好。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果仇恨無法挽回，我們最起碼可以利用它的熱量，澆築在卡茲戴爾的支架上。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而每一條生命，對於未來的卡茲戴爾，也許都很重要。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得倒簡單——", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#11$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們剛剛提到的，可以遠距離運送物資和人員的手段。這恐怕就是我們一直在調查的，軍事委員會在倫蒂尼姆的“生命線”。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會找到它，控制它。它既然能讓我們來到倫蒂尼姆，那麼……也能帶我們回家。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在所有人都被埋葬以前。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#8$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "埃芒加德", "content": "我……"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "埃芒加德", "content": "你未必會成功，你只是個僱傭兵。"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“讓所有人都有家可回。”", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "特蕾西婭。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我一直試圖把這個名字和這場戰爭分割開來。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "殿下，她……", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n一場和以前毫無區別的戰爭，又能讓誰安眠？", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "哈哈，大概是那混蛋特雷西斯弄的什麼障眼法，他殺了殿下，他還褻瀆了她。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n我會讓他跪下來道歉。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n等他道完歉，再把他的腦袋炸開花。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……和你接觸確實是正確的。我會把你的打算，以……巴別塔殘部的態度，告知巫妖們。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你們把我的小方塊炸了！你們讓我怎麼回去，靠走的？", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#7$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西北八公里的位置，有一個薩卡茲運輸營地，搶他們的車去吧。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "需要幫忙嗎？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……算了。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可不想再被她逮到一次，讓她發現我在和你們偷偷做什麼交易。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#6$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，祝你們好運，祝你們在見過她之後……還能活下來，達成你們的諾言。", "name": "埃芒加德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_869_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheelfts", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "“她”？", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n慢著。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們有沒有……一種熟悉的感覺？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#14$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "我在說什麼？我也不知道。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n真噁心，這種多愁善感的發言應該留給赫德雷。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "……可是，到底是什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "43_g8_wildernesswarcircle", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "不遠的地方，有個人坐在山頭。就在原本消散的那個幻象的邊緣。", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n她只是坐在那裡，好像什麼都沒在掛念。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n她的粉白色長髮從肩頭披下，一如往常。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_056", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "還有那種眼神，那種……悲傷的……", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "